###
#=========================================
# PERSONAL RECORD ROUTES
#=========================================

### POST /personal-records - Crear PR (reps)
POST {{baseUrl}}/personal-records HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken.response.body.data.token}}
content-type: application/json

{
	"exerciseId":"916135f4-4e11-43df-831e-5715f86879ad",
	"maxReps":13
}

### POST /personal-records - Crear PR (duration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/personal-records HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken.response.body.data.token}}
content-type: application/json

{
	"exerciseId":"07bd7be2-315c-48e2-b4b2-210161d79f2f",
	"maxDurationSeconds":20
}

### POST /personal-records - Crear PR (weight)
POST {{baseUrl}}/personal-records HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken.response.body.data.token}}
content-type: application/json

{
	"exerciseId":"f4d965c4-6b02-4917-89bc-b63cde23fa03",
	"maxWeight":40
}

### POST /personal-records - Mejorar un PR existente
POST {{baseUrl}}/personal-records HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken.response.body.data.token}}
content-type: application/json

{
	"exerciseId":"916135f4-4e11-43df-831e-5715f86879ad",
	"maxReps":12
}

### GET /personal-records/exercise/:exerciseId - Obtener PRs de un ejercicio específico
@exerciseId =916135f4-4e11-43df-831e-5715f86879ad
GET {{baseUrl}}/personal-records/exercise/{{exerciseId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken.response.body.data.token}}

